rows.label: qst200916_0010
rows.name: SHE'S BACK.

rows.label: qst200916_0020
rows.name: THE CURSED WITCH HAS COME.

rows.label: qst200916_0030
rows.name: Hello, everyone of the Tirkin tribe.

rows.label: qst200916_0040
rows.name: H-HELLO.

rows.label: qst200916_0050
rows.name: H-HELLO.

rows.label: qst200916_0060
rows.name:
For some reason, they're
more scared than before...

rows.label: qst200916_0070
rows.name:
We might be able to negotiate successfully
this time. Please leave it to me.

rows.label: qst200916_0080
rows.name:
I would like you to return the cargo you
stole from the Nopon merchant, Kupon-san.

rows.label: qst200916_0090
rows.name: DID WE HAVE SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

rows.label: qst200916_0100
rows.name: YOU'RE THE ONE WHO TOOK IT, RIGHT?

rows.label: qst200916_0110
rows.name:
If you return the cargo,
we will leave peacefully.

rows.label: qst200916_0120
rows.name: SHOULD WE RETURN IT...?

rows.label: qst200916_0130
rows.name:
IF WE DON'T, THE LIGHTNING
WILL COME AGAIN...

rows.label: qst200916_0140
rows.name:
We didn't come here to fight
with the Tirkin tribe... okay?

rows.label: qst200916_0150
rows.name: SHE'S BEING FRIENDLY?

rows.label: qst200916_0160
rows.name: WHAT DO WE DO? SHOULD WE BE FRIENDS?

rows.label: qst200916_0170
rows.name: OH NO, THE LIGHTNING IS COMING AGAIN.

rows.label: qst200916_0180
rows.name: WE MUST NOT ANGER THE CURSED WITCH.

rows.label: qst200916_0190
rows.name: QUICKLY, LET'S RETURN IT.

rows.label: qst200916_0200
rows.name:
Oh my... The weather has
coincidentally... again.

rows.label: qst200916_0210
rows.name: NO LIGHTNING.

rows.label: qst200916_0220
rows.name: WE'RE NOT RETURNING THE CARGO.

rows.label: qst200916_0230
rows.name: THAT'S RIGHT, THAT'S RIGHT.

rows.label: qst200916_0240
rows.name:
Hah... I suppose negotiations
have broken down.

rows.label: qst200916_0250
rows.name: Then we have no choice.
